Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.62,0:00:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切开始于神木
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.72,0:00:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断战斗\N不断祈求  不断寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从中产生了强烈的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.59,0:00:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全新的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.62,0:00:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光明的未来从现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.96,0:00:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得凶暴的七宝到处作乱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.13,0:00:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最强的敌人竟然就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.66,0:00:17.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉对七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法避免的宿命决斗即将展开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.84,0:00:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引导我们的最后一块碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.64,0:00:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枯井的另一边\N战国的世界里还有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.97,0:00:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战国时代的传说故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.24,0:00:27.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:25.15,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.32,0:00:34.20,OP,,0,0,0,,为谁而流的眼泪祈祷般地流下脸颊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.42,0:00:41.40,OP,,0,0,0,,不要隐藏脆弱 温柔地接受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.97,0:00:49.07,OP,,0,0,0,,连呼吸都忘记 眼中的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:56.07,OP,,0,0,0,,唯有太阳闪耀着不断寻找着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.07,0:01:03.30,OP,,0,0,0,,凝视镜子 你一定能看见立誓的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:10.60,OP,,0,0,0,,自己的背后也有翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.92,0:01:16.47,OP,,0,0,0,,你的改变 将改变世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.75,0:01:19.85,OP,,0,0,0,,实现梦想的爱的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:27.07,OP,,0,0,0,,穿越虚幻的海市蜃楼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.55,0:01:31.20,OP,,0,0,0,,天空有光 大地有水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.47,0:01:40.85,OP,,0,0,0,,坚强的心灵带你到未来的 ANGELUS（奉告祈祷）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.27,0:01:48.12,OP,,0,0,0,,双手握紧热情的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:25.15,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.34,0:02:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在追寻宿敌奈落的旅途中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.34,0:02:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来到彼世与此世的交界处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.84,0:02:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金钢枪破
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.57,0:02:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.50,0:02:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.28,0:02:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落要把最后的\N四魂之玉碎片夺走的阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.78,0:02:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后总算被成功阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  奈落接下来\N为了夺走桔梗的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.99,0:02:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放出了橱子鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.56,0:02:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要用此引诱出桔梗\N并且杀了她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.84,0:03:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为好不容易\N把桔梗这家伙给引出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔寄之树被腐蚀了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把橱柜给我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算会死也要保护橱柜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  你快醒醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我们总算\N设法解决了橱子鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是眼看着琥珀\N又成为奈落的帮凶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.77,0:03:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚的痛苦也越来越深
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.37,0:03:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.82,0:03:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会后悔保护琥珀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  要是不保护他的话\N我一定会更后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:08.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是所谓的人心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与往常一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卑劣的奈落\N躲在幕后不露面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是就在此时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们遭遇到一件\N与奈落有着重大关系的大事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪个家伙\N胆敢妨碍本大爷的美梦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第164话\N最强的敌人  被宿蛹控制的七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝这样不是很可怜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是吗  我很可怜耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题是这次发疯暴走的\N是狐妖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.22,0:05:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说狐妖是不会\N坐视小狐狸被欺负不管因而现身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道这是犬夜叉的诱敌计划
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是还是觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.99,0:05:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个办法有点太天真了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放我下来\N你到底把我当成什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正还是先把七宝放下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:52.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狐神大人来了\N请镇住他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来救我啊  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.99,0:06:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  现身了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来救小狐狸了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是它好像是要吃七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊  别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.87,0:06:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对付这种杂碎妖怪\N我两三下就可以劈了它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劈了他?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.44,0:06:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是拜托你\N压制住他就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.55,0:06:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉你先退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.28,0:06:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个家伙一定是狐神没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:45.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像被什么东西附了身的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭气弹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对鼻子很灵的妖怪应该会有作用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:07:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像对犬夜叉也起了作用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.11,0:07:14.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么狐神大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没事了\N邪气已经消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来应该会回神社去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了感谢你们\N我们准备好了饭菜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.67,0:07:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请各位到我们村长家休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你们的同伴\N似乎也很痛苦的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么今晚我们就借宿打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.51,0:07:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘了我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝\N你这小子不要慢吞吞的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快下来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天我要把你给搞哭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.39,0:07:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.35,0:07:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位狐神大人守护着这片土地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.36,0:07:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直供奉着他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以无论如何都不能杀死他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  请各位慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个我吃咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这小子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是有这个权力的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够吃到这顿饭\N也是多亏了七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.74,0:08:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  我的份也给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想一想还是不太放心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.91,0:08:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个附身的妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.55,0:08:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  你知道那个妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是叫作“宿蛹”的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然说不是很厉害的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.66,0:08:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是总是寄居在\N体型庞大的妖怪体内
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从来没听说过\N会附身于土地神身上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.40,0:08:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要调查看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是在追踪奈落吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是跟这种杂碎妖怪\N扯上关系的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有一点奈落的线索\N我就坐立难安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,性急坐不住\N不一直就是你的老毛病吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是因为今天没有出到风头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:08:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才一肚子不满吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.25,0:08:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能了解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要摆出一副什么都懂的蠢样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就是七宝这小子不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.46,0:09:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对…要把你搞哭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风还真大耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是鸟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.65,0:09:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宿…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宿蛹?难道还有别的宿蛹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要突然\N站在别人后面说话啦  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么害怕的话\N就给我乖乖躺下来睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不只一只吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:09:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:09:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  你也醒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到处都找不到七宝耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝刚刚挨了我一拳\N应该还躺在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:08.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的臭气弹  什么时候被他…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.87,0:10:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是宿蛹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道他被附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得追上去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像七宝这样的小妖怪\N要是被宿蛹附身的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母  追上七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.03,0:10:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝就拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.04,0:10:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝会像白天的土地神一样\N变得那么凶暴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:10:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为七宝\N已经输给宿蛹的邪气了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被他逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.15,0:11:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对要把你搞哭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.59,0:11:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为臭气弹的威力很大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.77,0:12:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.34,0:12:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们两个负责去找七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了  弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.95,0:12:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧  云母
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.29,0:12:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狐神大人终于平静下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.29,0:12:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就可以安心地干活了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.63,0:12:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.03,0:12:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.07,0:12:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是被很大的东西给弄出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.62,0:12:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被…被暗算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是谁做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.18,0:13:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁?谁在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救…救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真痛快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.95,0:13:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是黏鸟胶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师他们\N到现在都还没回来耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:07.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有新的妖怪出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请帮我们除掉他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的妖怪\N既然不是神仙就没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.47,0:14:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除掉他好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.47,0:14:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带着弓箭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有枪也带着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.81,0:14:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟…糟了\N再不快点找到七宝的话就惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村民们都快气炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的\N我的头才是快要爆炸了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.42,0:14:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.79,0:14:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要抢在大家的前面\N先找到七宝才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:37.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然就太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.16,0:14:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子好像已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让他逃了\N快拿枪射他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别着急  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.31,0:14:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.27,0:14:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是替身球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.79,0:15:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子他根本不打算\N乖乖束手就擒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之我们一定要\N抢在村民之前找到他才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然被你给看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.88,0:15:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了  快点给我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:37.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要帮你\N把背后的宿蛹拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招  狐火
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狐火这点小把戏\N对我除了觉得热以外根本不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:15:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毁灭陀螺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接锤球之后是呼唤陀螺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.05,0:16:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的狐妖术\N早就已经都被我看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有绝招没有使出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.77,0:16:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙\N有本事就尽管使出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种东西算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是拿他没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次真是倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝那小子\N比想象中还要难缠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有资格说我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.86,0:17:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:25.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  七宝好像又逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.13,0:17:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.39,0:17:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不能真的下狠招教训他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还跟他客气什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.93,0:17:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要揍他五  六十下\N让他清醒清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要他清醒\N不至于要打他五六十下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说这么暴力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  你拿那些丸子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.24,0:17:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里头下了迷药
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.31,0:17:46.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明就比我还要阴险嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,药起作用了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要逮住你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栗子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝又逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.02,0:18:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.39,0:18:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  你要杀了同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.83,0:18:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少罗唆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你以为你是小鬼\N我就会对你手下留情的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就大错特错了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.18,0:18:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.04,0:18:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.22,0:19:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝是被宿蛹附身了\N才会这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是嘛  就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.86,0:19:12.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还敢说“就是嘛  就是嘛”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:15.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你反应得太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是还记得自己\N刚才被附身的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难怪嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.37,0:19:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才老是对我用一些怪招
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.55,0:19:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少罗唆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不是因为你\N一次又一次的欺负我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说嘛\N你这小子果然都还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要赶快去追逃走的宿蛹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.73,0:19:44.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是在寻找新的寄生体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在放过它的话\N又会有人牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.81,0:19:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.79,0:20:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事啊  珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来应该寄生在\N庞大妖怪体内的宿蛹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会这么大规模的出现  就表示…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.76,0:20:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们原来的寄生体\N可能已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之\N我们只能先把这里收拾干净
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.04,0:20:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是宿蛹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.66,0:20:43.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近经常看到宿蛹出现
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.80,0:20:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宿蛹已经被消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.84,0:20:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道还有什么不放心的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那些宿蛹的数量来看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.21,0:21:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只死掉的寄生体\N应该是很大的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.44,0:21:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然寄生体死亡\N是很理所当然的事  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们却没有看见\N那个大妖怪的尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.19,0:21:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有气味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果寄生体没有死的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.02,0:21:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宿蛹无法再附身于寄生体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.26,0:21:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  难道你认为…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.96,0:21:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事情跟奈落有关
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.50,0:21:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然现在还不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是事情并不寻常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.97,0:21:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有错  这件事太可疑了
